\c 19
\s UJesu ugwetshelwa ukufa
\p
\v 1 Ngakho uPilatu wamthatha uJesu, wa\add m\add*tshaya ngesiswepu\x + Mat. 27.26. Mark. 15.15. Luka 23.16. Mat. 20.19. Mark. 10.34. Luka 18.33.\x*.
\v 2 Labebutho beluka umqhele wameva ba\add wu\add*beka ekhanda lakhe\x + Mat. 27.27-29. Mark. 15.16-18.\x*, bamgqokisa isembatho esiyibubende\x + 19.5. Hlu. 8.26.\x*,
\v 3 basebesithi: Bayethe, Nkosi yamaJuda! Basebemtshaya ngempama\x + 8.22.\x*.
\v 4 UPilatu wasebuya waphumela phandle, wathi kubo: Khangelani, ngiyamkhuphela phandle kini\x + 18.38.\x*, ukuze lazi ukuthi kangitholi lacala kuye\x + 19.6.\x*\x + 18.38.\x*.
\v 5 UJesu wasephumela phandle, ethwele umqhele wameva embethe isembatho esiyibubende. \add UPilatu\add* wasesithi kubo: Khangelani lumuntu!
\p
\v 6 Kwathi abapristi abakhulu labancedisi\x + 18.3. Mat. 26.58.\x* bembona, bamemeza bathi: Bethela, bethela! UPilatu wathi kubo: Mthatheni lina, li\add m\add*bethele; ngoba mina kangitholi cala kuye\x + 19.6.\x*.
\v 7 AmaJuda amphendula \add athi\add*: Silomlayo thina, langokomlayo wethu ufanele ukufa\x + Levi 24.16.\x*, ngoba uzenze iNdodana kaNkulunkulu\x + Mat. 26.66.\x*.
\v 8 Kwathi uPilatu esizwa lelolizwi, wesaba kakhulu\x + Mat. 27.19.\x*,
\v 9 wangena futhi endlini yombusi\x + 18.33. 19.1.\x*, wathi kuJesu: Uvela ngaphi wena\x + 7.27.\x*? Kodwa uJesu kamnikanga mpendulo\x + 18.37. Mat. 26.63.\x*.
\v 10 Khona uPilatu wathi kuye: Kawukhulumi lami yini? Kawazi yini ukuthi ngilamandla okukubethela, njalo ngilamandla okukukhulula?
\v 11 UJesu wamphendula \add wathi\add*: Ungeke ube lamandla phezu kwami\x + Luka 22.53. Joha. 7.30.\x*, uba ungawanikwanga\x + Roma 13.1.\x* evela phezulu\x + 3.3,7.\x*; ngakho onginikele kuwe ulesono esikhulu\x + 11.50. 18.14.\x*.
\v 12 Kusukela lapho uPilatu wadinga ukumkhulula. Kodwa amaJuda amemeza athi: Uba ukhulula lo, kawusuye umngane kaKesari; wonke ozenza inkosi, uphikisana loKesari\x + 18.33,36,37. Luka 23.2. Seb. 17.7.\x*.
\v 13 Kwathi uPilatu esizwa lelilizwi wamkhuphela phandle uJesu\x + 19.9.\x*, wahlala phansi esihlalweni sokwahlulela, endaweni ebizwa ngokuthi Gandelwe ngaMatshe\x + Mat. 27.19.\x*, kodwa ngesiHebheru yiGabatha\x + 19.17,20. Seb. 21.40.\x*;
\v 14 njalo kwakungamalungiselelo ephasika\x + 19.31,42. 18.28. Mat. 27.62.\x*, njalo kwakungaba \w lihola\w** lesithupha\x + 4.6. Mark. 15.25.\x*; wasesithi kumaJuda: Khangelani inkosi yenu\x + 19.18,19,21.\x*!
\v 15 Kodwa amemeza \add athi\add*: Susa, susa, mbethele\x + Luka 23.18. Seb. 21.36.\x*! UPilatu wathi kuwo: Ngibethele yini inkosi yenu? Abapristi abakhulu baphendula \add bathi\add*: Kasilankosi ngaphandle kukaKesari\x + Gen. 49.10. 1 Sam. 12.12.\x*.
\v 16 Ngakho wasemnikela kubo, ukuze abethelwe\x + Mat. 27.26. Mark. 15.15. Luka 23.25. Joha. 18.36.\x*. Basebemthatha uJesu ba\add m\add*qhuba\x + Mat. 27.31. Mark. 15.20. Luka 23.26.\x*.
\s Ukubethelwa lokufa kukaJesu
\p
\v 17 Kwathi ethwele isiphambano\x + Luka 14.27.\x* sakhe waphuma waya endaweni ethiwa \add yiNdawo\add* yokhakhayi\x + Mat. 27.32,33. Mark. 15.22. Luka 23.33. Nani 15.36. Heb. 13.12. Joha. 19.20.\x*, ethiwa ngesiHebheru yiGolgotha;
\v 18 lapho abambethela khona, labanye ababili kanye laye, ngapha langapha, loJesu ephakathi\x + Mat. 27.38. Mark. 15.27. Luka 23.32,33.\x*.
\v 19 UPilatu wasebhala lesaziso, wa\add si\add*phanyeka esiphambanweni; njalo kwakubhalwe \add ukuthi\add*: UJESU UMNAZARETHA INKOSI YAMAJUDA\x + Mat. 27.37. Mark. 15.26. Luka 23.38.\x*.
\v 20 Lalesisaziso abanengi bamaJuda basifunda, ngoba indawo lapho uJesu ayebethelwe khona yayiseduze lomuzi\x + Mat. 27.32,33. Mark. 15.22. Luka 23.33. Nani 15.36. Heb. 13.12. Joha. 19.20.\x*; njalo kwakubhalwe ngesiHebheru, ngesiGriki, \add la\add*ngesiRoma\x + Luka 23.38.\x*.
\v 21 Abapristi abakhulu bamaJuda basebesithi kuPilatu: Ungabhali \add ukuthi\add*: INkosi yamaJuda; kodwa ukuthi lo wathi: NgiyiNkosi yamaJuda.
\v 22 UPilatu waphendula \add wathi\add*: Engikubhalileyo, ngikubhalile\x + Gen. 43.14. Esta 4.16.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Kwathi abebutho, sebembethele uJesu\x + Mat. 27.35. Mark. 15.24. Luka 23.34.\x*, bathatha izembatho zakhe, basebezenza izabelo ezine, ngulowo lalowo owebutho waba lesabelo\x + Seb. 12.4.\x*, lesigqoko; kodwa isigqoko sasingelamthungo\x + Eks. 28.32.\x*, selukiwe sonke kusukela phezulu.
\v 24 Ngakho bakhulumisana besithi: Kasingasidabuli, kodwa asisenzele inkatho, ukuthi sizakuba ngesikabani; ukuze kugcwaliseke umbhalo othi: Babelana izembatho zami, benza inkatho yokuphosa ngesigqoko sami\x + Hlab. 22.18.\x*. Azenza-ke lezizinto amabutho.
\p
\v 25 Kwakumi esiphambanweni sikaJesu unina, lodadewabo kanina\x + Mat. 27.55,56. Mark. 15.40. Luka 23.49.\x*, uMariya\x + Mat. 27.56.\x* \add um\add*kaKlophasi, loMariya Magadalena\x + Luka 24 18.\x*.
\v 26 Ngakho uJesu ebona unina, lomfundi amthandayo emi khona\x + 13.23.\x*, wathi kunina: Mama, khangela indodana yakho\x + 2.4.\x*.
\v 27 Emva kwalokho wathi kumfundi: Khangela unyoko. Kusukela ngalelohola lowomfundi wamthatha wamusa kwakhe\x + 16.32.\x*.
\p
\v 28 Emva kwalokhu uJesu ekwazi ukuthi konke kwasekuphelile, ukuze kugcwaliseke umbhalo\x + Hlab. 69.21.\x*, wathi: Ngomile.
\v 29 Kwakubekwe isitsha sigcwele iviniga\x + Luka 8.16.\x*; basebegcwalisa uzipho ngeviniga\x + Mat. 27.48. Mark. 15.36. Luka 23.36.\x*, ba\add lu\add*hloma \w kuhisope\w**, ba\add lu\add*sa emlonyeni wakhe\x + Mat. 27.48. Mark. 15.36. Eks. 12.22.\x*.
\v 30 Kwathi-ke uJesu elemukele iviniga, wathi: Kuphelile\x + 17.4.\x*; wasekhothamisa ikhanda, wanikela umoya\x + 1 Pet. 2.23. Mat. 27.50. Mark. 15.37. Luka 23.46. Joha. 10.18.\x*.
\p
\v 31 Ngakho amaJuda, ngoba kwakungamalungiselelo\x + Mark. 15.42. Joha. 19.14,42.\x*, ukuze izidumbu zingahlali esiphambanweni ngesabatha\x + Dute. 21.23.\x* (ngoba lolosuku lwesabatha lwalulukhulu\x + Eks. 12.16.\x*), acela uPilatu ukuthi yephulwe imilenze yabo, njalo basuswe.
\v 32 Ngakho abebutho beza, bephula imilenze yowokuqala leyomunye ababebethelwe laye;
\v 33 kodwa sebefika kuJesu, kwathi bebona ukuthi wayesefile, kabayephulanga imilenze yakhe;
\v 34 kodwa omunye webutho wamgwaza ngomkhonto ehlangothini, njalo kwahle kwaphuma igazi lamanzi\x + 1 Joha. 5.6,8.\x*.
\v 35 Yena owabonayo ufakazile, njalo ubufakazi bakhe buqinisile, yena-ke uyazi ukuthi ukhuluma okuliqiniso, ukuze lina likholwe\x + 21.24.\x*.
\v 36 Ngoba lezizinto zenzeka ukuze kugcwaliseke umbhalo \add othi\add*: Kakuyikwephulwa thambo lakhe\x + Eks. 12.46. Nani 9.12. Hlab. 34.20. 1 Kor. 5. 7.\x*.
\v 37 Njalo lomunye umbhalo uthi: Bazamkhangela abamgwazileyo\x + Zek. 12.10. Isam. 1.7.\x*.
\s Ukungcwatshwa kukaJesu
\p
\v 38 Kwathi emva kwalezizinto uJosefa weArimathiya\x + Mat. 27.57-61. Mark. 15.42-47. Luka 23.50-56.\x*, owayengumfundi kaJesu, kodwa ngasese ngenxa yokwesaba amaJuda\x + 7.13.\x*, wacela kuPilatu ukuthi asuse isidumbu sikaJesu; futhi uPilatu wavuma. Ngakho weza wasisusa isidumbu sikaJesu.
\v 39 Kwasekusiza loNikodima\x + 3.1.\x*, owafika kuJesu kuqala ebusuku, ephethe inhlanganiso\x + Mark. 16.1. Luka 23.56. 24.1.\x* \w yemure\w**\x + Eks. 30.23. Esta 2.12. Hlab. 45.8. Zaga 7.17. Mat. 2.11. Mark. 15.23.\x* lenhlaba\x + Hlab. 45.8. Zaga 7.17. Nani 24.6.\x* engaba amaphawundi alikhulu\x + 12.3.\x*.
\v 40 Basebesithatha isidumbu sikaJesu, basibopha ngamalembu acolekileyo kanye lamakha\x + 11.44. Seb. 5.6.\x*, njengomkhuba wamaJuda wokungcwaba\x + Mat. 26.12.\x*.
\v 41 Njalo kwakukhona kuleyondawo ayebethelwe khona isivande, lesivandeni kwakulengcwaba elitsha, okwakungazange kubekwe muntu kulo.
\v 42 Basebembeka lapho uJesu ngenxa yamalungiselelo amaJuda, ngoba ingcwaba laliseduze\x + 19.14,31.\x*.